fields.title: Pico de Gallo
fields.description: (Mexican) Green, White and Red. A spoonful of Mexico in every bite!
fields.instructions:
1. Chop all ingredients.
  2. mix together.
  3. Serve with tortilla chips.

fields.title: Guacamole
fields.description: (Mexican) Avocado, lime, and cilantro. A creamy delight!
fields.instructions:
1. Mash avocados.
  2. Mix in other ingredients.
  3. Serve with tortilla chips.

fields.title: Salsa Verde
fields.instructions:
1. Roast tomatillos and jalape単os.
  2. Blend with cilantro and lime juice.
  3. Serve with tortilla chips.

fields.title: Roti
fields.instructions:
1. Mix flour, water, and salt to form a dough.
  2. Roll into flat circles.
  3. Cook on a hot griddle until puffed and golden.

fields.title: Naan
fields.instructions:
1. Mix ingredients to form a dough.
  2. Let rise, roll into flat circles, and cook in a tandoor or on a hot griddle.

fields.title: Kheer (Indian Rice Pudding)
fields.description: (Indian) A creamy, sweet rice pudding flavored with cardamom and garnished with nuts.
fields.instructions:
1. Cook rice in milk until soft.
  2. Add sugar and cardamom.
  3. Garnish with nuts and serve warm or chilled.

fields.title: Chole Bhature
fields.description: (Indian) Spicy chickpeas served with deep-fried bread.
fields.instructions:
1. Cook chickpeas with spices.
  2. Make dough for bhature, roll out, and deep fry.
  3. Serve together.

fields.title: Paneer Butter Masala
fields.instructions:
1. Cook tomatoes and spices to make a sauce.
  2. Add paneer and cream.
  3. Serve with naan or rice.

fields.title: Tacos
fields.description: (Mexican) Soft or hard shell filled with your choice of meat and toppings.
fields.instructions: 1. Cook meat, fill tortillas, and top with desired ingredients.

fields.title: Burrito
fields.description: (Mexican) Flour tortilla wrapped around a filling of rice, beans, and protein.
fields.instructions:
1. Cook rice and beans.
  2. Fill tortillas with rice, beans, and protein.
  3. Roll up and serve.

fields.title: Enchiladas
fields.description: (Mexican) Rolled tortillas filled with your favourite protein and topped with a spicy tomato sauce, creme fraiche and tangy feta cheese.
fields.ingredients:
• Tortillas
  • Meat (chicken, beef) or veg protein (mushrooms, tofu)
  • Enchilada sauce
  • Creme fraiche
  • Feta cheese
fields.instructions:
1. Fill tortillas with meat, roll up, and place in a baking dish.
  2. Top with enchilada sauce, creme fraiche and cheese.
  3. Bake until bubbly.
